28 ða gecneowlecan to minum mode;
29 and hnigan ða hand to his ansyne,
30 andswarode: "Sind ge her, la Ser Brunetto?"

34 Ic cwæð to him: "Swa ic mæg, ic wille cuman;
35 and gif ðu wille ðæt ic mid ðe sitte,
36 ic ðæt do, gif him licað ðe ic mid fare."

40 Forðæm ga ofer: ic ðe wille cuman to ðæm wætere;
